<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:13:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普的净资产达到 65 亿美元，成为世界 500 名最富有的人之一</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-net-worth-hits-6-5-billion-making-him-one-of-worlds-500-richest-people/articleshow/108773598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;州上诉法院将特朗普在纽约欺诈诉讼中必须缴纳的保证金从 5 亿多美元大幅减少至 1.75 亿美元。与此同时，特朗普媒体与科技集团完成了一项持续 29 个月的合并，导致特朗普拥有目前价值为数十亿。因此，特朗普的净资产飙升超过40亿美元，使他首次跻身彭博亿万富翁指数前500名。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 01:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-net-worth-hits-6-5-billion-making-him-one-of-worlds-500-richest-people/articleshow/108773598.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚 130 多名被绑架学童在被囚禁数周后正在返回家园</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-130-abducted-schoolchildren-in-nigeria-are-returning-home-after-weeks-in-captivity/articleshow/108773498.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773498.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 3月7日，这些孩子在偏远的卡杜纳州库里加镇的学校被骑摩托车的枪手劫持，引发了广泛的营救行动。他们周日在邻近扎姆法拉州以北约 200 公里（超过 120 英里）的森林中被军方救出，不过当局没有提供救援细节，也没有透露是否有绑架嫌疑人被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-130-abducted-schoolchildren-in-nigeria-are-returning-home-after-weeks-in-captivity/articleshow/108773498.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯告诉调解人它将坚持停火的最初立场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-on-ceasefire/articleshow/108773452.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773452.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-on-ceasefire/articleshow/108773452.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的 X Corp 在针对仇恨言论监管机构的诉讼中败诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musks-x-corp-loses-lawsuit-against-hate-speech-watchdog/articleshow/108773444.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773444.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国旧金山地区法官查尔斯·布雷耶 (Charles Breyer) 表示，“显然”马斯克的 X 公司起诉了反数字仇恨中心 (CCDH)，因为他不喜欢该中心的批评，并认为该中心的研究会损害 X 的形象并吓跑广告商。布雷耶写道：“X Corp 提起此案是为了惩罚 CCDH 批评 X Corp 的出版物，或许也是为了劝阻其他可能希望参与此类批评的人。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:01:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musks-x-corp-loses-lawsuit-against-hate-speech-watchdog/articleshow/108773444.cms</guid></item><item><title>遏制：欧盟开始调查谷歌、苹果的应用商店规则</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/reining-in-eu-begins-probe-into-app-store-rules-of-google-apple/articleshow/108773246.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773246.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/reining-in-eu-begins-probe-into-app-store-rules-of-google-apple/articleshow/108773246.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙法官暂停 Telegram 服务</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-judge-halts-suspension-of-telegram/articleshow/108773330.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773330.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:11:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-judge-halts-suspension-of-telegram/articleshow/108773330.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会首次要求加沙“立即”停火，美国弃权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-demands-cease-fire-in-gaza-during-muslim-holy-month-of-ramadan-its-1st-demand-to-halt-fighting/articleshow/108769909.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108769909.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国安理会周一首次要求停止战斗，要求在穆斯林斋月期间在加沙停火。该决议还要求释放哈马斯 10 月 7 日在以色列南部发动突然袭击时被扣押的所有人质。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-demands-cease-fire-in-gaza-during-muslim-holy-month-of-ramadan-its-1st-demand-to-halt-fighting/articleshow/108769909.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁中国网络间谍公司</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-sanctions-chinese-cyber-espionage-firm/articleshow/108773370.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773370.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-sanctions-chinese-cyber-espionage-firm/articleshow/108773370.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对纽约罚款提出上诉，债券削减68%至1.75亿美元</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-bond-cut-by-68-to-175-million-as-he-appeals-ny-fine/articleshow/108773381.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773381.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一作出这一决定之际，特朗普面临最后期限，要么支付 4.54 亿美元的判决金，要么交纳 120% 判决金额的保证金，以便在上诉期间搁置判决。这将相当于近 5.45 亿美元，比特朗普所说的他手头的现金还要多。这位前总统有 10 天的时间来交纳新的保证金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-bond-cut-by-68-to-175-million-as-he-appeals-ny-fine/articleshow/108773381.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜表示日本首相希望会见金正恩</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-says-japans-kishida-showed-intention-to-meet-kim-jong-un-recently/articleshow/108760629.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108760629.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹金与正透露，日本首相岸田文雄已表示有兴趣通过其他沟通渠道与朝鲜领导人举行会面。据官方媒体朝中社报道，金正恩强调，双边关系的未来取决于日本做出实际政治决定的能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-says-japans-kishida-showed-intention-to-meet-kim-jong-un-recently/articleshow/108760629.cms</guid></item><item><title>针对30岁以下人群的中国广告引发争议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-ad-for-under-30s-triggers-row/articleshow/108773402.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773402.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:27:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-ad-for-under-30s-triggers-row/articleshow/108773402.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宣布投入60亿美元清理重工业</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-announces-6-billion-to-clean-up-heavy-manufacturing/articleshow/108773406.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773406.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据周一的一份声明，曾是前总统唐纳德·特朗普贸易战的主要受益者的世纪铝业公司将获得多达 5 亿美元的资金来建设该设施。这将使该国目前国内能源密集型金属的生产规模增加一倍，同时预计还能减少 75% 的排放量。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:29:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-announces-6-billion-to-clean-up-heavy-manufacturing/articleshow/108773406.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国称中菲关系正处于海上事件的“十字路口”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-says-relations-with-philippines-at-crossroads-amid-maritime-incidents/articleshow/108773411.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773411.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国周一警告菲律宾要谨慎行事并寻求对话，称两国关系正处于“十字路口”，两国海岸警卫队之间因海事主张而发生的新对抗加剧了紧张局势。这是中国外交部三个月内第二次发出此类警告，当时两国就南沙群岛的领土主张发生公开争执。南沙群岛是南海的一个无人居住的群岛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:34:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-says-relations-with-philippines-at-crossroads-amid-maritime-incidents/articleshow/108773411.cms</guid></item><item><title>令人惊讶的是，欧洲一项主要气候保护计划在农民抗议后被搁置</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/in-a-surprise-move-a-major-european-climate-protection-plan-is-shelved-following-farmer-protests/articleshow/108773421.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108773421.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;经过欧盟机构迷宫数月的审理后，成员国本应于周一最终批准该法案。但原本只是一个橡皮图章的东西现在却变成了可能永久搁置的东西。 “每个人都清楚，存在着巨大的僵局。考虑到即将举行的选举，摆脱这种僵局并不容易，”荷兰气候部长罗布·杰滕说。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/in-a-surprise-move-a-major-european-climate-protection-plan-is-shelved-following-farmer-protests/articleshow/108773421.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普赢得暂停 4.54 亿美元民事欺诈裁决，避免资产被扣押</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-wins-pause-of-454-million-civil-fraud-ruling-averting-asset-seizures/articleshow/108770863.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108770863.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 周一赢得了一项诉讼，如果他在 10 天内缴纳 1.75 亿美元的较小金额的保证金，就可以暂停其 4.54 亿美元的民事欺诈判决，这是这位美国前总统的胜利，阻止了纽约州当局采取措施扣押他的资产。中级州上诉法院的裁决缓解了特朗普严重的现金短缺问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 17:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-wins-pause-of-454-million-civil-fraud-ruling-averting-asset-seizures/articleshow/108770863.cms</guid></item><item><title>伦敦高等法院将于周二做出朱利安·阿桑奇上诉裁决</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/julian-assange-appeal-ruling-to-be-given-by-london-high-court-on-tuesday/articleshow/108770786.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108770786.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伦敦高等法院将于周二就维基解密创始人朱利安·阿桑奇是否可以就从英国引渡到美国提出上诉做出裁决。这一决定标志着阿桑奇在英国司法系统内的法律斗争的一个潜在的关键时刻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/julian-assange-appeal-ruling-to-be-given-by-london-high-court-on-tuesday/articleshow/108770786.cms</guid></item><item><title>一艘满载罗兴亚难民的船在印度尼西亚倾覆几天后又发现了六具尸体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/six-more-bodies-are-found-days-after-a-boat-of-rohingya-refugees-capsized-off-indonesia/articleshow/108770744.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108770744.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;地方当局周一表示，上周一艘载有 150 多人的船倾覆后，在印度尼西亚附近海域又发现了六具罗兴亚难民的尸体。搜救官员在一份声明中说，这六名妇女的尸体是在亚齐省海岸发现的。周末发现了五具尸体。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:35:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/six-more-bodies-are-found-days-after-a-boat-of-rohingya-refugees-capsized-off-indonesia/articleshow/108770744.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯欢迎联合国安理会呼吁加沙停火的决议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-welcomes-un-security-council-resolution-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire/articleshow/108770696.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108770696.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯周一表示，欢迎联合国安理会呼吁加沙停火的决议，并准备立即与以色列交换囚犯。周一通过的决议要求以色列和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰组织哈马斯立即停火，并在美国投弃权票后立即无条件释放所有人质。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:29:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-welcomes-un-security-council-resolution-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire/articleshow/108770696.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国法院提起诉讼，质疑 EB-5 投资者签证费和庇护费上涨</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/lawsuit-filed-in-us-court-challenging-visa-fee-hikes-for-eb-5-investors-and-asylum-fee-charges/articleshow/108770644.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108770644.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国法院提起诉讼，挑战 EB-5 投资者签证费用的上涨，包括大幅增加初始申请费用和取消条件。原告寻求停止费用变更，强调了对适当的规则制定程序和费用合法性的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/lawsuit-filed-in-us-court-challenging-visa-fee-hikes-for-eb-5-investors-and-asylum-fee-charges/articleshow/108770644.cms</guid></item><item><title>100多名被绑架的尼日利亚学生返回卡杜纳</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-100-kidnapped-nigerian-students-arrive-back-in-kaduna/articleshow/108769878.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108769878.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 131名学生获释，1名教职员工死亡； 137 名人质在卡杜纳获救；向扎姆法拉州发送赎金；信息部长否认支付赎金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-100-kidnapped-nigerian-students-arrive-back-in-kaduna/articleshow/108769878.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>